metadata.name: "Donne-moi allumette.…"
metadata.description:
Feel this smell...as your nerves begin to feel the air…
This is the usual flow in which you are...which penetrates you and sticks its fiery knives…
You are very close to burnout... 
Well... 
Maybe this is what you really need...what you deserve at this moment in time…
Say the last words...do the last action...and burn...burn...burn…

* The match lights up…
The fire is burning up…
Inhale...exhale...burn…
